The evidence with the title 'Hospital 'facility fees' boosting medical bills, and not just for hospital ... ' says Dec 20, 2012  ... Because the center was owned by Baptist Health South Florida , the hospital- based system slapped a $275 facility fee on top of the $233 doctor's bill. The woman 's insurance refused to pay half the fee and Romaniello argued she would have gone elsewhere had she known about the extra fees beforehand . 
